race.comment: TITAN RISING (2) was just treading water until last start where he took up the running and was only caught late in the race. He's drawn a better gate this time and the claim of Catarino comes in handy. Can find the front once again and will be hard to run down. REIGN IN THE CASH (3) steps out to 2000m for the first time today but he looks well placed on what he's done in recent efforts. He just missed in a photo finish last start when flying late over the mile. Needs some luck from the draw, but with improvement expected now, he'll take plenty of beating. SHE'SATROOPER (7) finished off strongly behind REIGN IN THE CASH last start when settling midfield in the run. She ended up 1.7L off the winner, but is another who looks suited by the rise in trip. Should be in the finish again. WIFE SAYS YES (8) is ready for this trip now and a much better run is anticipated. KIRRILY (5) was too good last start when beating some of these rivals and can land the knockout blow again.
